              <format attr='background-color' value='#ffffff' />
            </zone-style>
          </zone>
          <zone h='87368' id='7' param='horz' type-v2='layout-flow' w='29209' x='0' y='12632'>
            <zone fixed-size='416' forceUpdate='true' h='84504' id='9' is-fixed='true' type-v2='text' w='27599' x='805' y='14064'>
              <formatted-text>
                <run fontcolor='#000000' fontsize='10'>In contrast to garden waste,HDPE shows no repeating seasonal pattern at all — no reliable peak quarter, no calendar story to point to. What it does show is a steady, consistent rise: every single quarter across two full years moved in the same direction. That consistency is exactly what separates a real underlying change from a seasonal wobble — and it&apos;s the reason this material, out of dozens checked, earned a place in this story.</run>
              </formatted-text>
              <zone-style>
                <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
                <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
                <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
                <format attr='margin' value='4' />
              </zone-style>
            </zone>
            <zone-style>
              <format attr='border-color' value='#c0c0c0' />
              <format attr='border-style' value='solid' />
              <format attr='border-width' value='1' />
              <_.fcp.DashboardRoundedCorners.true...format attr='corner-radius' value='5' />
              <format attr='margin' value='5' />
              <format attr='padding' value='5' />
              <format attr='background-color' value='#ffffff' />
            </zone-style>
          </zone>
