                <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                <run fontcolor='#000000' fontsize='12'>  + Clean up Data from imported Data regarding special characters</run>
                <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                <run fontcolor='#000000' fontsize='12'>  + Transform Authorities fields to connect Map, Waste and Population Tables</run>
                <run>Æ&#10;</run>
